measureElements.name: Artifact_Recognizer
measureElements.body: ((isOCLTypeOf(kdm:code::MethodUnit) or ( isOCLTypeOf(kdm:code:CallableUnit) and ( CallableKind = 'external' or CallableKind = 'stored' or CallableKind = 'regular'))) and name <> '')

measureElements.name: AFPSharedArtifacts_Recognizer
measureElements.body: ( CallingAndReferencingGraph()->exists(h1 | h1.isOCLOfType(AFPTransactionHead)) and CallingAndReferencingGraph()->exists(h2 | h2.isOCLOfType(AFPTransactionHead)) and h1 <> h2)

measureElements.name: AddedTransactionalAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and not AFPTransactionHead()->exists(h | h.isInPreviousRevision and h.evolvedTo = self))

measureElements.name: DeletedTransactionalAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: (isInPreviousRevision and not AFPTransactionHead()->exists(h | h.isInLatestRevision and h.evolvedFrom = self))

measureElements.name: AFPDataWithChangedType_Recognizer
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and ((EIF()->includes(self) and ILF()->exists(d | d.isInPreviousRevision and d.evolvedTo = self)) or (ILF()->includes(self) and EIF()->exists(d | d.isInPreviousRevision and d.evolvedTo = self )))

measureElements.name: SplitDataAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: (d1, d2: DET | d1 <> d2 and self.ownedElement().includes(d1) and not self.ownedElement().includes(d2) and not self.isInPreviousRevision and DataAFP()->exists(l | l.isInPreviousRevision and l.ownedElement().includes(d1.evolvedFrom) and l.ownedElement().includes(d2.evolvedFrom) ) )

measureElements.name: MergedDataAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: ( ownedElement()->exists(d1, d2: DET | not self.isInPreviousRevision and self.ownedElement().includes(d2) and self.ownedElement().includes(d1) and DataAFP()-exists(l1, l2 | l1 <> l2 and l2.ownedElement().includes(d2.evolvedFrom) and l1.ownedElement().includes(d1) ) ) )

measureElements.name: AddedDataAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: ( isInLatestRevision and not DataAFP()->exists(d | d.isInPreviousRevision and d.evolvedTo = self))

measureElements.name: DeletedDataAFP_Recognizer
measureElements.body: ( isInPreviousRevision and not DataAFP()->exists(d | d.isInLatestRevision and d.evolvedFrom = self))

measureElements.name: CallOrReferenceActions
measureElements.body: ((isOCLOfType(kdm:action::CallableRelations) or isOCLOfType(kdm:action::DataRelations) or isOCLOfType(kdm:code::Extends) or isOCLOfType(kdm:code::Implements)) and from = self)

measureElements.name: CallingOrReferencingActions
measureElements.body: ((isOCLOfType(kdm:action::CallableRelations) or isOCLOfType(kdm:action::DataRelations) or isOCLOfType(kdm:code::Extends) or isOCLOfType(kdm:code::Implements)) and to = self)

measureElements.name: isAddedArtifact
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and not FromRevision()->exists(a: Artifacts | a.evolvedTo = self))

measureElements.name: isDeletedArtifact
measureElements.body: (isInPreviousRevision and not ToRevision()->exists(a: Artifacts | a.evolvedFrom = self))

measureElements.name: isUpdatedArtifact
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and ToRevision()->exists(a: Artifact | a.evolvedTo = self and self.source <> a.source))

measureElements.name: isAddedDET
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and not FromRevision()->exists(d: DET| d.evolvedTo = self))

measureElements.name: isDeletedDET
measureElements.body: (isInPreviousRevision and not ToRevision()->exists(d: DET | d.evolvedFrom = self))

measureElements.name: isUpdatedDET
measureElements.body: (isInLatestRevision and ToRevision()->exists(d: DET | d.evolvedTo = self and self.type <> d.type))

measureElements.name: UpdatedDataAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: IF DETChangeRatio <= 1/3 THEN 0.25; IF 1/3 < DETChangeRatio <= 2/3 THEN 0.50; IF 2/3 < DETChangeRatio <= 1 THEN 0.75; IF DETChangeRatio > 1 THEN 1;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Updated Data AFP to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points, based on the DET Change Ratio

measureElements.name: DataAFPWithChangedTypeComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real changedTypeCF = 0.40 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Data AFP with Changed Type (EIF to ILF or ILF to EIF) to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: MergedDataAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real mergedCF = 0.40 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Data AFP resulting from the merge of Data AFP from the previous / initial revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: SplitDataAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real splitCF = 0.40 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Data AFP resulting from the split of a Data AFP in the previous / initial revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: DeletedDataAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real deletedCF = 0.40 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Deleted Data AFP from previous / initial revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: AddedDataAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real addedCF = 1 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Added Data AFP in latest / final revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: DeletedTransactionalAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real deletedCF = 0.40 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Deleted Transactional AFP from previous / initial revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: AddedTransactionalAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: { Real addedCF = 1 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Complexity Factor to use to weight Added Transactional AFP in latest / final revision to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points

measureElements.name: RawUpdatedTransactionalAFPComplexityFactor
measureElements.formula: IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 0 THEN 0.25; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 1 THEN 0.50; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 2 THEN 0.75; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 3 THEN 1.00; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 4 THEN 1.25; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 5 THEN 1.50; IF sRatioEffortComplexity = 6 THEN 1.75;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Raw Complexity Factor to use to weight Updated Transactional AFP to get the resulting Automated Enhancement Function Points, based on the Effort Complexity Net Variation Ratio and the Processed Effort Complexity Ration, before the capping based on the Ratio of Shared Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wRatioEffortComplexityProcessed
measureElements.formula: IF RatioEffortComplexityProcessed <= 1/3 THEN 0; IF 1/3 < RatioEffortComplexityProcessed <= 2/3 THEN 1; IF 2/3 < RatioEffortComplexityProcessed <= 1 THEN 2; IF RatioEffortComplexityProcessed > 1 THEN 3
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of the Processed Effort Complexity Ratio in the Raw Complexity Factor of Updated Transactional AFP

measureElements.name: wRatioEffortComplexityTotalVariation
measureElements.formula: IF RatioEffortComplexityTotalVariation <= 1/3 THEN 0; IF 1/3 < RatioEffortComplexityTotalVariation <= 2/3 THEN 1; IF 2/3 < RatioEffortComplexityTotalVariation <= 1 THEN 2; IF RatioEffortComplexityTotalVariation > 1 THEN 3;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of the Effort Complexity Net Variation Ratio in the Raw Complexity Factor of Updated Transactional AFP

measureElements.name: capRatioSharedEffortComplexity
measureElements.formula: IF RatioShareEffortComplexity = 1 THEN 0.25; IF 1 > RatioShareEffortComplexity >= 3/4 THEN 0.50; IF 3/4 > RatioShareEffortComplexity >= 1/2 THEN 0.75; IF 1/2 > RatioShareEffortComplexity THEN 2;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Cap value for the Complexity Factor of Updated Transactional AFP based on the Shared Effort Complexity Ratio

measureElements.name: ArtifactEffortComplexity
measureElements.formula: IF VeryHighEC THEN { Real wVeryHighEC = 1.2 }; IF HighEC THEN { Real wHighEC = 0.7 }; IF ModerateEC THEN { Real wModerateEC = 0.2 }; IF LowEC THEN { Real wLowEC = 0.1 }
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Effort Complexity value of an Artifact based on its Effort Complexity Level

measureElements.name: ArtifactEffortComplexityIndex
measureElements.formula: IF ( ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^0 = 2^0 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^1 = 2^1 AND ( ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^2 = 2^2 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^3 = 2^3 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^4 = 2^4 ) THEN 3 ELSE IF ( ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^5 = 2^5 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^6 = 2^6 OR (ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^10 = 2^10 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^11 = 2^11 AND (ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^2 = 2^2 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^3 = 2^3 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^4 = 2^4 )) OR (ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^7 = 2^7 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^8 = 2^8 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^9 = 2^9 ) ) THEN 2 ELSE IF ( ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^10 = 2^10 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^11 = 2^11 OR (ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^15 = 2^15 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 65536 = 65536 AND ( ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^7 = 2^7 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^8 = 2^8 OR ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^9 = 2^9 )) OR (ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^12 = 2^12 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^13 = 2^13 AND ArtifactEffortComplexityValue & 2^14 = 2^14 )) THEN 1 ELSE 0 ;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Decoding of contributing bits into an aggregated Effort Complexity Index ranging from 0 to 3

measureElements.name: wArtifactLackOfCommentLevel
measureElements.formula: IF VeryHighLackOfComment THEN 2^4; IF HighLackOfComment THEN 2^9; IF ModerateLackOfComment THEN 2^14; IF LowLackOfComment THEN 2^19
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Contribution bit of the Lack of Comment level into the overall Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wArtifactLinesOfCodeLevel
measureElements.formula: IF VeryLargeLinesOfCode THEN 2^3; IF LargeLinesOfCode THEN 2^8; IF MediumLinesOfCode THEN 2^13; IF SmallLinesOfCode THEN 2^18
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Contribution bit of the Lines Of Code level into the overall Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wArtifactCouplingLevel
measureElements.formula: IF VeryHighCoupling THEN 2^2; IF HighCoupling THEN 2^7; IF ModerateCoupling THEN 2^12; IF LowCoupling THEN 2^17
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Contribution bit of the inbound Coupling level into the overall Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wArtifactSQLComplexityLevel
measureElements.formula: IF VeryHighSQLComplexity THEN 2; IF HighSQLComplexity THEN 2^6; IF ModerateSQLComplexity THEN 2^11; IF LowSQLComplexity THEN 2^16
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Contribution bit of the SQL Complexity level into the overall Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wArtifactCyclomaticComplexityLevel
measureElements.formula: IF VeryHighCyclomaticComplexity THEN 1; IF HighCyclomaticComplexity THEN 2^5; IF ModerateCyclomaticComplexity THEN 2^10; IF LowCyclomaticComplexity THEN 2^15
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Contribution bit of the Cyclomatic Complexity level into the overall Effort Complexity

measureElements.name: wArtifactNumberOfUpdateSQLStatement
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactNumberOfUpdateSQLStatement > { Integer maxUpdateSQLStatement = 0 } THEN { Integer wUpdateSQLStatement = 10 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of an Update SQL query into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact

measureElements.name: wArtifactNumberOfGroupBySQLStatement
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactNumberOfGroupBySQLStatement > { Integer maxGroupBySQLStatement = 0 } THEN { Integer wGroupBySQLStatement = 0 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of a SQL query with a Group By into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact

measureElements.name: wArtifactNumberOfSQLSubqueries
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactNumberOfSQLSubqueries > { Integer maxSQLSubqueries = 0 } THEN { Integer wSQLSubqueries = 10 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of a SQL subquery into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact

measureElements.name: wArtifactNumberOfUsedSQLTableColumns
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactNumberOfUsedSQLTableColumns > { Integer maxSQLTableColumns = 9 } THEN { Integer wSQLTableColumns = 10 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of a SQL query on too many columns into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact

measureElements.name: wArtifactNumberOfUsedSQLTables
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactNumberOfUsedSQLTables > { Integer maxSQLTables = 30 } THEN { Integer wSQLTables = 10 } ;
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of SQL queries on too many tables into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact

measureElements.name: wArtifactMaxNumberOfSQLTablesPerQuery
measureElements.formula: IF ArtifactMaxNumberOfSQLTablesPerQuery > { Integer maxSQLTablesPerQuery = 4 } THEN { Integer wSQLTablesPerQuery = 50 };
measureElements.shortshortDescription: Weight of presence of a SQL query on too many tables into the overall SQL Complexity of an Artifact
